cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.SY

This paper discusses the expressivity and training of deep neural networks, which are topics commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of Hilbert space and activation function design also suggests a focus on mathematical analysis and optimization, which is relevant to the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SY, and cs.SI, in that order.
